data.description: SELLERS OFFERING 10K TOWARDS BUYER'S CLOSING COSTS!! This could cover a 2/1 rate buydown!!  Beautiful 5 bedroom 2.5 bath home in the highly desired Cumberland Estates! This home features a main level open floor plan. Family and friends can hang out in the kitchen, while catching a game over the beautiful stone fireplace. Main floor also features a flex room, perfect for an office or formal dining/sitting area. Upstairs features a whopping 5 bedrooms. 5th bedroom can also be used as a rec room. Primary bath features an upgraded tiled, frameless glass shower, as well as tiled floors and granite tops. SO MUCH SPACE, the options are ENDLESS. Once in the backyard, you will quickly notice this home is sitting on a PREMIUM lot! Not only does it have a fully fenced in back yard (sides are privacy), but it also backs up to woods, full of nature and wildlife! Covered back patio! Schedule your showing ASAP as this home will not last long!
